N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 650.3 - Rules of commission to control in case of conflict

State Regulations

The rules and regulations of the commission are supplemental
to the laws, rules and regulations of the States of New York and Vermont, except where they are in conflict and in such case the rules and regulations of
the commission shall control. Notes
